Young, Appellant, v. Young, Appellee.

[Cite as Young v. Young (1994), 70 Ohio St.3d 679.]

(No. 94-1220 Submitted September 13, 1994 Decided November 9, 1994.) Gretchen K Beers and Ann Ratcliff, Miami County Child Support Enforcement Agency, for appellant. Louie R. Kindell & Associates and Louie R. Kindell, for appellee.

*680The discretionary appeal is allowed; the judgment of the court of appeals is reversed and the judgment of the court of common pleas is reinstated on the authority of Cramer v. Petrie (1994), 70 Ohio St.3d 131, 637 N.E.2d 882.

Moyer, C.J., A.W. Sweeney, Douglas, Wright, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney and Pfeifer, JJ., concur.
